delegation to watch local elections in China.
</P>
<P>
Charles Costello, the head of the group, said that they had
seen that representatives are given the freedom of choice in
accordance with the law. During their visit, he said, officials
and the people were very friendly and frank and free to speak
their minds and that they were pleased with their openness.
</P>
