<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, January 12 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results in
the 750,000 US dollars Sydney International tennis at White City
on Tuesday (prefix number denotes seeding):
</P>
<P>
Men's first round:
</P>
<P>
Thomas Muster, Austria, bt Jonas Bjorkman, Sweden, 7-5, 6-7
(2/7), 6-3
</P>
<P>
