(7/1), 6-1
</P>
<P>
Jason Stoltenberg, Australia, bt Alberto Berasategui, Spain,
6-1, 6-7 (3/7), 7-6 (7/5)
</P>
<P>
3-Carlos Moya, Spain, bt Thomas Johansson, Sweden, 6-3, 7-6
(7/4)
</P>
<P>
Gustavo Kuerten, Brazil, bt 5-Greg Rusedski, Britain, 1-6,
6-3, 6-4
</P>
<P>
8-Todd Martin, United States, bt Hicham Arazi, Morocco, 6-1,
6-3
