Milliyet (National):
</P>
<P>
-- Referring to a Turkish warrant for the extradition of
Abdullah Ocalan, leader of the outlawed Kurdish Workers' Party
(PKK), Italian Prime Minister Massimo D'alema said Monday that
Italy is a state of law and one can not be arrested by the request
of a government.
</P>
