<HEADLINE> Hingis Advances to Third Round of Sydney Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, January 12 (Xinhua) -- Former world No.1 Martina
Hingis of Switzerland spent 55 minutes to beat Australian
wildcard entrant Alicia Molik 6-1, 6-2 and advanced to third
round of the Sydney International tennis tournament on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
