<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, January 11 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 468.33 points Monday, down 0.04 percent from last week's
finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 193,849 shares changed
hands in 175 deals, and the turnover was 856,506 dinars (778,641
U.S. dollars). 
</P>
